## Local testing:

# Setup env via:
ml use ~lfricadmin/lmod
ml lfric

# Build via
./build/local_build.py jedi_lfric_tests

# Run via:
OMP_NUM_THREADS=1 mpiexec -np 6 ../bin/jedi_forecast configuration.nml
#NOTE: There apears to be an issue with this configuration when run with 1 PE. 
#      6 MPI ranks seems to work fine so testing with that for now.